  <md:title>Further Reading</md:title>
  <md:abstract>Did you enjoy Professor Brennan's guide "Introduction to Political Philosophy"? Check out these great books on justice, liberty, and political authority.</md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>34f73548-f9e9-49fe-bcff-422d9d7cc662</md:uuid>
